comment("First, I need to find the nearest stone furnace to use for smelting")
stone_furnace_position = nearest('stone-furnace')
comment("I will move to the furnace location to start the smelting process")
move_to(stone_furnace_position)
comment("I will place a burner mining drill on the nearest iron ore spot to start mining it for smelting.")
